@startuml
title Pollution Monitoring System - Authentication and Dashboard Access

autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Auth API" as AuthAPI
participant "verifyToken Middleware" as VerifyToken
participant "User Repository" as UserRepo
participant "Dashboard API" as DashboardAPI
participant "KPI Service" as KPI
participant "Reading Service" as ReadingSvc
participant "Alert Service" as AlertSvc

User -> Frontend : submit email + password
Frontend -> AuthAPI : POST /api/auth/login
AuthAPI -> UserRepo : find user + verify password
UserRepo --> AuthAPI : user record
AuthAPI --> Frontend : access token + refresh cookie

User -> Frontend : open dashboard
Frontend -> DashboardAPI : GET /api/auth/me or KPI/alerts/readings
DashboardAPI -> VerifyToken : authorize request
VerifyToken -> UserRepo : load current role and assignments
UserRepo --> VerifyToken : req.user context
VerifyToken --> DashboardAPI : allowed
DashboardAPI -> KPI : compute summary
DashboardAPI -> ReadingSvc : get latest readings
DashboardAPI -> AlertSvc : get scoped alerts
KPI --> DashboardAPI : KPI payload
ReadingSvc --> DashboardAPI : readings payload
AlertSvc --> DashboardAPI : alerts payload
DashboardAPI --> Frontend : dashboard data

alt access token expired
  Frontend -> AuthAPI : POST /api/auth/refresh
  AuthAPI --> Frontend : new access token
  Frontend -> DashboardAPI : retry original request
end

@enduml